List of Components

	1.	Navbar
	•	Navigation menu for the application.
	2.	Footer
	•	Bottom section of the page with copyright and links.
	3.	Button
	•	Reusable button with customizable properties.
	4.	Modal
	•	Overlay dialog for messages or forms.
	5.	Card
	•	Display of related information in a visually appealing format.
	6.	Form
	•	Reusable form structure for user input.
	7.	Input
	•	Custom input fields with validation.
	8.	Loading Spinner
	•	Visual indicator of loading states.
	9.	Notification / Alert
	•	Message or alert to inform users of actions.
	10.	Breadcrumbs
	•	Navigation aid to show user location in the hierarchy.
	11.	Sidebar
	•	Vertical navigation or information panel.
	12.	Image Gallery
	•	Display of images in a grid or carousel format.
	13.	Tabs
	•	Navigation for switching between different content sections.
	14.	Table
	•	For displaying data in rows and columns.
	15.	Pagination
	•	Component for navigating through paginated content.
	16.	Accordion
	•	Expandable sections for displaying content.
	17.	Checkbox Group
	•	Group of checkboxes for multiple selections.
	18.	Radio Button Group
	•	Group of radio buttons for single selections.
	19.	Select Dropdown
	•	Dropdown for selecting options.
	20.	Range Slider
	•	Input for selecting a value from a range.
	21.	Search Bar
	•	Input field for searching content.
	22.	Avatar
	•	Display of user profile pictures.
	23.	Progress Bar
	•	Indicator for progress on tasks.
	24.	Tooltip
	•	Small pop-up for additional information on hover.
	25.	Date Picker
	•	Input for selecting dates.
	26.	Time Picker
	•	Input for selecting time.
	27.	Calendar
	•	Component for displaying a calendar view.
	28.	Quote
	•	Display of quotes or testimonials.
	29.	Social Media Links
	•	Links or icons for social media profiles.
	30.	Feature List
	•	List of features or benefits.